# 🐾 Smart Animal Rescue System

## Overview

This project simulates a distributed smart system to support the UN SDG "Life on Land".

It uses gRPC services and JmDNS for service discovery.

---

## Services

* Animal Detection Service
* Rescue Coordination Service
* Veterinary Service

---

## Technologies

* Java
* gRPC
* Protocol Buffers
* JmDNS

---

## Status

Project setup started. Implementing Animal Detection Service.

